description: This dataset contains the number of New York State live births by the infant’s birth weight in grams and the mother’s county of residence. The data presented here may not be the same as the Vital Statistics tables on the DOH public web due to data updates. For more information, check out: :http://www.health.ny.gov/statistics/vital_statistics/ or go to the "About" tab.
